{
  "texts": [
    "Overall, this research contributes to the advancement of agricultural technology by presenting a robust and efficient solution for the early detection of tomato leaf diseases.",
    "The study showcases the effectiveness of both pre-trained models and custom-designed CNN architectures, providing valuable insights for researchers and practitioners in the field of agriculture and deep learning.",
    "A custom CNN architecture was designed and employed as a benchmark.",
    "The researchers explored different well-known pre-trained CNN models, such as ResNet, VGG, Inception, and MobileNet, among others.",
    "These models were fine-tuned on a dataset containing images of plant leaves with various diseases."
  ]
}